 time. Abraham is playing a pimp in the film. His character is a leader of a gang that controls the shadow business. [ 25 ] Abraham was included in the panel of judges for the âMiss Germanyâ? beauty pageant in 2012 and 2013. [ 26 ] On January 9, 2013, the RA Ministry of Diaspora hosted a presser for Abraham. Minister Hranush Hakobyan praised Abraham as a role model and awarded him the "Poghos Nubar" medal. [ 27 ] [ 28 ] Abraham sent a letter of condolence on the death of Vladimir Yengibaryan to his family. [ 29 ] Awards [ edit ] Hrant Shahinyan Medal [ 30 ] 2009 Berlin Sportsman of the Year [ 31 ] Child Award 2009 [ 32 ] See also [ edit ] List of IBF world champions List of WBO world champions List of middleweight boxing champions List of super middleweight boxing champions Reigning boxing champions References [ edit ] ^ Portrait von Arthur Abraham | Offizielle Website von Arthur Abraham . Arthur.eeedv.de (2011-08-18). Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ Alexander Abraham â Boxer â Boxing news . Boxnews.com.ua. Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ Biofile with Arthur Abraham . Thebiofile.com (2010-11-24). Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ Arthur Abraham Getting Married in Armenia . tarlani.com. June 17, 2011 ^ Arthur Abraham Back In Action On January 14th | HyeFighters â Armenian Combat Sports . HyeFighters (2011-11-17). Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ Arthur Abraham wants to marry in Armenia â Tert.am â News | Armenia | Russia | CIS | World . Tert.am (2011-06-17). Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ Arthur Abraham vs. Jermain Taylor â Boxrec Boxing Encyclopaedia . Boxrec.com. Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ Abrahamâs Intensity Determination Impress Mike Tyson | BoxingInsider.com â Boxing | Boxing News . BoxingInsider.com (2009-10-27). Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ The Ring Top 100 | Ringtv.craveonline.com | Blog . Ringtv.craveonline.com. Retrieved on 2012-01-16. [ dead link ] ^ Iole, Kevin. (2010-03-05) Unbeaten Abraham seeks U.S. stardom â Boxing â Yahoo! Sports . Sports.yahoo.com. Retrieved on 2012-01-14. ^ Bo